---
// src/pages/reviews/best-headphones-2026.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Best Headphones 2026 - Buying Guide">
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">Audio</span>
      <h1>Best Headphones 2026: Our Top Picks</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By ReviewCloud</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 6, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Our Top Picks</h2>
      <p>We've tested the best headphones of 2026. Here are our favorites for every budget and use case.</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>🎧 Best Overall: AirPods Pro 3</h2>
      <p>Apple's latest AirPods Pro deliver exceptional noise cancellation, improved battery life, and seamless integration with Apple devices.</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> $249</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🏆 Best Noise Cancellation: Sony WH-1000XM6</h2>
      <p>Sony's flagship headphones offer the best noise cancellation we've ever tested. Perfect for travelers and commuters.</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> $399</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>💰 Best Value: AirPods 4</h2>
      <p>Great sound quality at an affordable price. Excellent choice for iPhone users who don't need Pro features.</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> $129</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🎮 Best for Gaming: AirPods Max</h2>
      <p>Apple's over-ear headphones deliver premium sound and build quality. Great for gaming and immersive audio.</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> $549</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How to Choose</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>In-ear vs Over-ear:</strong> In-ear for portability, over-ear for comfort</li>
        <li><strong>Noise Cancellation:</strong> Essential for travel</li>
        <li><strong>Battery Life:</strong> Look for 20+ hours</li>
        <li><strong>Platform:</strong> Consider your phone/电脑</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="buy-links">
      <h3>Shop Headphones</h3>
      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=headphones&tag=rc0440-20" class="buy-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
        Best Headphone Deals on Amazon
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: white; }
  .review-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .category { background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .review-header h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .meta { color: #666; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center; }
  .toc { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #555; }
  .buy-links { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; }
  .buy-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 3rem; background: #ff9900; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
